-- RWE Wins Bid to Build World’s Biggest Offshore Wind Farm in U.K.
-- B y   S a l l y   B a k e w e l l
-- 2013-07-11T10:37:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-11/rwe-wins-bid-to-build-world-s-biggest-offshore-wind-farm-in-u-k-.html
RWE AG (RWE)  won approval from the U.K.
government to spend 3.6 billion pounds building the world’s
largest offshore wind farm off the nation’s east coast.  The Department of Energy & Climate Change also said
construction will start on the Pen y Cymoedd Wind Farm in South
Wales. That project led by Vattenfall AB involves 400 million
pounds of investment. The department made a statement about the
projects on its website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
